{"tid":434980,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"其實卡卡西夠唔夠左助打？","createTime":"2017-10-13T21:05:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-17T08:56:24.000Z","uid":80736,"like":3,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"099fae0a358bbcf8b7fe281f9739b7f431908c95","tid":434980,"uid":80736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T21:05:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/14/050327_95b1121ab80eabeb001f2396ab8c161f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F14%2F050327_95b1121ab80eabeb001f2396ab8c161f.jpg&h=1e6e0e21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢一期講到卡卡西有能力對付左助咁，但佢被左助一招都被得咁辛苦，唔知以死相迫，好似3代咁，有冇得打？<br />\n<br />\n雖然電切勁過千島。。。"},{"pid":"f0bffca4361b29a6f5b6d7c1506a25cf8c83d4e7","tid":434980,"uid":117821,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T23:39:29.000Z","msg":"電切 你重新睇過套漫畫先再問野啦"},{"pid":"fc69ff7815688508a2a49e6b508315cd69cc12cd","tid":434980,"uid":142725,"like":10,"dislike":7,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T23:42:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">雷切勁過千鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"28eb2fba8692857032afe0607a64d5bcaf1652da","tid":434980,"uid":43575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T23:43:37.000Z","msg":"卡卡西無左隻寫輪眼點會夠打喎"},{"pid":"91c00c912f5a347c1669d346fd16e22aa2a300f7","tid":434980,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T23:45:32.000Z","msg":"冇神威嘅卡卡西係垃圾"},{"pid":"ba00323d19b4c6774f1e6f4a408e37bf399997de","tid":434980,"uid":1646,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T23:51:28.000Z","msg":"柒柒西只會柒住黎走"},{"pid":"dec2253cefda2630274be2140bd07c7faf70d32c","tid":434980,"uid":40286,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T00:05:59.000Z","msg":"火影一直講嘅都唔係個人能力為主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每個角色都勝在有身邊嘅羈絆"},{"pid":"4362d5e3609f8d0e9df57102406e541060be01aa","tid":434980,"uid":141582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T00:16:08.000Z","msg":"呢個情景表面得卡卡西<br />\n實際仲有鳴門<br />\n不過需要留意返小櫻呢隻內鬼<br />\n整體黎講 應該夠打<br />\n<br />\n時間一直往後推的話<br />\n卡卡西隻揪隻穩輸"},{"pid":"8da97e57477e85e80951aff8f27ff43be35956af","tid":434980,"uid":31323,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T00:28:33.000Z","msg":"有名你叫旗木五五開 super算唔算夠打？"},{"pid":"80260bf26c25ffbb24da952257b5fbcd7314f88b","tid":434980,"uid":99028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T01:08:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1d09937fa28165051b929b67b4545ac916ed12e3","tid":434980,"uid":64131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T01:51:57.000Z","msg":"果陣佐助好似就盲"},{"pid":"681d4310c92e45a843c296f747b49bf1f85ecb34","tid":434980,"uid":82404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T02:18:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有名你叫旗木五五開 super算唔算夠打？</blockquote><br />\n同帶土打55波，但係又唔夠培因打係咩料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢只係同冇得穿透既帶土55波咋"},{"pid":"1f177beb79624b281ef78371116f63f8c5d2629b","tid":434980,"uid":80736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T02:41:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個情景表面得卡卡西<br />\n實際仲有鳴門<br />\n不過需要留意返小櫻呢隻內鬼<br />\n整體黎講 應該夠打<br />\n<br />\n時間一直往後推的話<br />\n卡卡西隻揪隻穩輸</blockquote><br />\n但佢叫明門走先，似係有對策"},{"pid":"4d7b726940556905ca55ae802a98692b825bc06f","tid":434980,"uid":80736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T02:41:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有名你叫旗木五五開 super算唔算夠打？</blockquote><br />\n同帶土打55波，但係又唔夠培因打係咩料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n能力想克啫"},{"pid":"bb776640a5649353d7ef762d16395c4d9d9665ef","tid":434980,"uid":37223,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T02:43:44.000Z","msg":"有名你叫旗木五五開 <br />\n上至輝夜下至再不斬佢都係打和"},{"pid":"1690ece258b9a8e6a75684d6de9ecd89b59e8fa1","tid":434980,"uid":4683,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T08:22:45.000Z","msg":"一定夠 <br />\n因為連登好多人都話 <br />\n雷切係勁過千鳥"},{"pid":"55e05a71dc0acc36270bcb8b6f6cfa88a0deef0f","tid":434980,"uid":48428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T12:37:22.000Z","msg":"張圖個時卡卡西隻眼仲係度<br />\n佐助又盲咁濟<br />\n有機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7027a9c589a957117f1001306333d05ac85b3e1","tid":434980,"uid":55964,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T13:01:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有名你叫旗木五五開 super算唔算夠打？</blockquote><br />\n同帶土打55波，但係又唔夠培因打係咩料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解到而家都仲有人以為卡卡西打贏帶土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n帶土係專登比卡卡西用千鳥隊落個心度，目的係消除班所設既咒印<br />\n同當年琳既做法一樣<br />\n兩個互插個陣帶土仲專登留手冇插落卡卡西要害"},{"pid":"ad0f2aa842350bc735e8457efa2d9ccd4c5a8920","tid":434980,"uid":89337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T13:04:53.000Z","msg":"柒西：留係到你地會見到唔想見既野<br />\n可能就係驚鳴仔見到mk助殺左柒西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e52b0f35a6b412cbd977d518af9e508702ae1426","tid":434980,"uid":30673,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T13:05:30.000Z","msg":"本身呢期左右覺得佐助真係好難返到轉頭<br />\n結果之後就開始膠"},{"pid":"d5853c64a0785da03d637c8739ccb8ac1214441c","tid":434980,"uid":55964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T13:08:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/14/210847_5895c8bb4531a911ea82db573470be8d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F14%2F210847_5895c8bb4531a911ea82db573470be8d.jpg&h=8d998034&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/20